---
import Footer from '@components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '@components/Header.astro';
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import Merch from '@components/Merch.astro';
---
<Layout title="merch-collection">
  <body>
    <div class="my-container">
      <Header />
      <main>
        <div class="flex h-[75%] mt-2">
          <div class="container post">
            <div class="inner">
              <div class="page-title">
                <h2>
                  Merch Collection
                </h2>
                <div>
                  <p>Collection of merch from my days going to shows.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="merch-container">
                    <Merch img="v1650332839/m19y.dev/IMG_1817_lp9zrh_qnix3y.webp" />
                    <Merch img="v1650332840/m19y.dev/IMG_1818_ux6jxg_bnvvmk.webp" />
                    <Merch img="v1650332839/m19y.dev/IMG_1824_vhede3_l4gm9l.webp" />
                    <Merch img="v1650332840/m19y.dev/IMG_1825_usrqyv_p8ggsq.webp" />
                    <Merch img="v1650332840/m19y.dev/IMG_1826_higudb_j0ogti.webp" />
                    <p>Picked up both of these shirts at the Ottobar 9/10/2010.</p>
                    <p>Full show roster: Bane, TUI, Cruel Hand, Alpha & Omega.</p>
                    <a target="_blank" href="https://res.cloudinary.com/shoveltoss-com/image/upload/v1650332840/m19y.dev/IMG_2071_ctztu0_yezu5l.webp">
                      <img alt="" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/shoveltoss-com/image/upload/v1650332840/m19y.dev/IMG_2071_ctztu0_yezu5l.webp" />
                    </a>
                    <p>From a show in 2010 (?) with Terror, Gravemaker, Foundation, Naysayer and Violent Side.</p>
                    <Merch img="v1650332840/m19y.dev/IMG_2366_ik6tzf_uzlhxi.webp" />
                    <p>Look like this was from  Sunday, July 3rd 2011. Lineup: Dead End Path, Free Spirit, United Youth, Mob Mentality, Black Rations</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
      <Footer />
    </div>
  </body>
</Layout>
<style>
  li {
    color: white
  }
  img {
    width: 80%;
    padding: 2px;
  }
  img:hover {
    cursor: pointer
  }
</style>